events.title: Amherst Invite Hotel
events.description:
(413) 549-6000

Where can I park when I arrive on campus?
Enter the Campus Center Parking Garage. Get a ticket on the way in and park on the 2nd Level of the garage. Then walk into the concourse via the hallway and take the elevators to the 3rd level (Hotel Lobby).

Is there a fee for parking in the Campus Center Parking Garage?
We offer unrestricted in/out parking to all our guest for a nominal fee of $6 per night. Tickets are validated upon check-in and can be used up until 5 pm on the day of your departure. If your parking pass is misplaced you will charged an additional $6 fee per night to replace it. Certain group/departmental rates (may) include complimentary parking. Please contact the Hotel main desk at 877-822-2100, to confirm. Garage restriction is 7‚Äô2‚Äù.
